<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/index/style_index_announce.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>

  
<%- include('../partials/user_partials/nav_index') %>

  <div class="about-header">
    <div class="about-header__inner">
      <p class="section-tag">공지 사항</p>
      <h1 class="about-header__title">새로운 소식을 전해드립니다</h1>
      <p class="about-header__sub">서비스 업데이트, 점검 안내, 이용 정책 변경 등 중요한 내용을 확인하세요.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br><br><br><br><br>


  <div class="notice-list">

    <% notices.forEach(function(notice) { %>
    <div class="notice-item">
      <span class="notice-badge <%= notice.isNew ? 'new' : '' %>"><%= notice.category %></span>
      <span class="notice-title"><%= notice.title %></span>
      <span class="notice-date"><%= notice.date %></span>
    </div>
    <% }); %>

  </div>
</main>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
  </div>



<br>
<br>
<br>
<br><br><br><br><br>
<br>

<br>
<footer>
  © 2025 <span>복약안심서비스</span> | Team Jetson5 | 스마트 약상자 기반 복약 관리 플랫폼
</footer>

</body>
</html>
